import React from 'react'
import { Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

function UploadImages() {
  return (
    <>
    <input class="custom-file-input" type="file" accept='image/*'/>
      <Button
        variant="primary" 
        className="mb-3" 
        type="button">
      </Button>
      </>
  )
}

export default UploadImages
